WEBVTT

00:02.500 --> 00:04.301
Kids, the day you get married is supposed

00:04.301 --> 00:06.104
To bethe happiest day of your life,

00:06.204 --> 00:08.907
The perfect ending to a perfect love story.

00:09.106 --> 00:11.509
My wedding-- at least my first wedding--

00:11.509 --> 00:13.011
Didn't go so well.

